00:03:35.190 --> 00:03:42.837
So we will make the requirement
that the total probability to

00:03:42.837 --> 00:03:46.788
find it anywhere add up to 1.
 

00:03:46.788 --> 00:03:50.943
That is a convention
because--well,

00:03:50.943 --> 00:03:52.900
in some sense.
 

00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:54.990
It's up to you how you want to
define probability.

00:03:54.990 --> 00:03:58.617
You say, "What are the
odds I will get through this

00:03:58.617 --> 00:04:00.068
