00:31:42.140 --> 00:31:45.318
How do I find the coefficients?
 

00:31:45.318 --> 00:31:48.390
Suppose I write the vector
V as e_1

00:31:48.390 --> 00:31:51.194
times V_1 
e_2 times

00:31:51.194 --> 00:31:53.630
V_2
e_3 times

00:31:53.630 --> 00:31:55.058
V_3.
 

00:31:55.058 --> 00:31:55.858
Don't worry
e_1,

00:31:55.858 --> 00:31:57.160
e_2 and
e_3 are the

00:31:57.160 --> 00:31:58.773
usual guys,
e_1 is

00:31:58.773 --> 00:32:01.148
i, e_2
