properties,

00:32:29.003 --> 00:32:30.900
i⋅i is
1.

00:32:30.900 --> 00:32:33.009
That's the same as
j⋅j.

00:32:33.009 --> 00:32:35.019
That's the same as
k⋅k.

00:32:35.019 --> 00:32:37.323
And that
i⋅k

00:32:37.323 --> 00:32:39.315
and
i⋅j

00:32:39.315 --> 00:32:40.558
are 0 and so on.
 

00:32:40.558 --> 00:32:44.198
Namely the dot product of one
guy with himself is 1,

00:32:44.198 --> 00:32:46.910
and any one with anything else
is 0.

00:32:46.910 --> 00:32:49.674
That just tells you they all
have unit length and they're

00:32:49.674 --> 00:32:50.910
