00:32:50.910 --> 00:32:53.372
I want to write this as
e_i

00:32:53.372 --> 00:32:55.771
⋅
e_j,

00:32:55.771 --> 00:32:57.730
but this could be 1,2 or 3.
 

00:32:57.730 --> 00:32:59.078
That could be 1,2 or 3.
 

00:32:59.078 --> 00:33:02.278
I want to say this is equal to
