00:33:02.920 --> 00:33:07.046
This is equal to 0 if
i is not equal to

00:33:07.046 --> 00:33:07.920
j.
 

00:33:07.920 --> 00:33:09.900
This is a usual vector analysis.
 

00:33:09.900 --> 00:33:13.210
I'm just saying the dot product
of basis vectors has this

00:33:13.210 --> 00:33:14.972
property,
1 if they match,

00:33:14.972 --> 00:33:18.374
