so there's a shortcut for this

00:33:18.374 --> 00:33:21.592
and that's write the symbol
δ_ij.

00:33:21.592 --> 00:33:24.925
δ_ij is
called Kronecker's

00:33:24.925 --> 00:33:25.568
delta.
 

00:33:25.568 --> 00:33:30.828
Kronecker's in a lot of things,
but this is one place where his

00:33:30.828 --> 00:33:33.288
name has been immortalized.
 

00:33:33.288 --> 00:33:35.769
He just said instead of saying
this all the time,

00:33:35.769 --> 00:33:37.380
1 if they're equal,
0 if they're different,

00:33:37.380 --> 00:33:40.290
why don't you call it my
