the indices are equal the right

00:33:53.452 --> 00:33:56.160
hand side is 1,
indices are unequal right hand

00:33:56.160 --> 00:33:56.808
side is 0.
 

00:33:56.808 --> 00:34:00.425
Do you understand that this
gives you the fact that each

00:34:00.425 --> 00:34:04.239
